    'xer.meta1': '🎤 Open talk',
    'xer.p': 'A conversation about <strong>adapted basketball and its transformative power</strong>: how the game breaks barriers for people with physical functional diversity — wheelchair users — and for people with intellectual diversity. Because the right to play belongs to everyone, no exceptions.',
