    'crowd.h2a': 'Collaborate with a project that', 'crowd.h2b': 'changes lives',
    'crowd.intro': 'We want to build a covered basketball court in Badalona: a space where everyone can play with dignity. People with reduced mobility, people with intellectual diversity, families with limited resources. Free, adapted and open to the entire community. And we want to create Badalona\'s first adapted basketball team.',
