    'carm.h2': 'The <span class="accent">Carmelites Descalços</span> court',
    'carm.p1': 'The Discalced Carmelite Fathers of Badalona have lent us their court a few days a week. We take care of the maintenance and improve it together.',
    'carm.p2': 'More than a court: an <strong style="color:white;">open space for everyone</strong>, with special focus on people with reduced mobility, functional diversity and vulnerable groups.',
