    'carm.c1.h4': 'Spread the word', 'carm.c1.p': 'Share the project on social media, tell people around you and help us grow. Every share opens new doors.',
    'carm.c2.h4': 'Volunteer', 'carm.c2.p': 'We need hands to paint, improve and bring the court to life. If you have time and energy, you\'re welcome. Write to us and we\'ll explain how to join.',
    'carm.c3.h4': 'Financial support', 'carm.c3.p': 'Every contribution goes directly to improving the court: paint, hoops, accessibility. If you want to help, get in touch and we\'ll explain how.',
    'carm.cta.p': 'Want to join the Carmelites project? Whether as a volunteer, a financial supporter or simply by spreading the word — write to us and we\'ll tell you how to get involved.',
