    'inc.lead': 'Because basketball knows no barriers. We promote <strong>adapted basketball</strong> as a tool for inclusion and life — so that any person, with any physical or intellectual ability, can play with dignity, equality and joy. No exceptions.',
    'inc.p1.h4': 'Accessible courts', 'inc.p1.p': 'We promote wheelchair-friendly access on all neighbourhood courts: ramps, flat surfaces and adapted spaces so no one is left out.',
    'inc.p2.h4': 'Free sessions', 'inc.p2.p': 'We run free basketball sessions for people with intellectual diversity — a space for play, teamwork and life where everyone shines at their own pace.',
